high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the kitchen island
Pick up the nearest knife from the counter
Turn right and walk around the kitchen island to face the sink
Cut the tomato in the sink with the knife
Turn left and walk around to face the kitchen island above the oven
Put the knife down on the kitchen island
Turn left and walk back to the kitchen sink
Pick up a slice of tomato from the sink
Turn left and walk forward to the microwave
Cook the tomato in the microwave and then remove it
Turn left and walk forward then turn left to face the kitchen island
Put the tomato slice down on the kitchen island
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked tomato slice on the kitchen island

high_descs: Turn around to the right and go to the island.
Pick up the closest chef's knife to you.
Turn and go to the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Turn and go to the island above the oven.
Set the chef's knife on top of the other chef's knife.
Go back to the sink behind you.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Move to the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave.
Take the heated tomato slice to the island above the oven.
Set the tomato clice down to the right of the chef's knife.
anns.task_desc: Set a heated tomato slice on the island.

high_descs: Turn right, walk three steps forward and then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife next to the loaves of bread.
Turn right and to the sink.
Use the knife to slice the tomato in the sink.
Turn left toward the microwave then turn right and to the knife on the counter.
Put the knife down so it is resting on the other knife with the bladed end touching the salt shaker.
Turn left and go back to the sink.
Pick up the middle piece of sliced tomato.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside, turn it on then take the tomato out and close it.
Turn left and walk back to the knives on the counter.
Put the tomato slice down so it is standing up in front of the black kettle.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife plus a slice of tomato on the counter by the other knife and black kettle.
